On Friday also the case of Adrian Zielinski , the London Olympic champion in the class up to 85 kg , was tested positive for the anabolic steroid Nandrolon three days earlier , like his brother Tomasz .
Both deny taking it , but are not allowed to start in the class up to 94 kg .
