The IAAF had banned the entire Russian team from starting on the grounds of systematic doping , with the exception of the runner nation Kenya , which also produces a lot of bad news in Rio .
In swimming , previous offences in China also caused a fierce confrontation between athletes .
Camille Lacourt , the French , attacked the Chinese Olympic champion Sun Yang harshly .
